gh", "timestamp": 1775008319}, {"author": "thecosmicflamingo", "author_id": "1192693833", "id": "18385584442091514", "text": "Omg yes. Can you please do some of the greatest speeches from films? 🙏🏻\n- Gladiator\n- Seven\n- Lion King\n- Interstellar\n- Forrest Gump\nEtc 🌸", "timestamp": 1774696888}, {"author": "euyndara", "author_id": "32727734917", "id": "17958508080084603", "text": "🗣️🗣️🗣️🗣️😂😂😂", "timestamp": 1774238715}, {"author": "_mariya_zaharova_", "author_id": "9179305711", "id": "17928959619228340", "text": "I imagine Rosencrantz and Guildenstern standing right at his door listening to this and be like \"😃\"", "timestamp": 1773171975}, {"author": "alyviaspam08", "author_id": "72549896584", "id": "18002288336854131", "text": "Bro sounds like Severus Snape", "timestamp": 1771522381}, {"author": "frankie.scherer", "author_id": "63758745082", "id": "18335844871244096", "text": "Sounds like my brother in the videos he used to take on my moms phone as a kid", "timestamp": 1771101922}, {"author": "celioeliosouza", "author_id": "6463558483", "id": "17876596026487459", "text": "Tamo com tempo hein irmão?", "timestamp": 1771085680}, {"author": "issi444_", "author_id": "3115914103", "id": "18075883514092710", "text": "What Snape sounds like on the Harry Potter movies.", "timestamp": 1771032415}, {"author": "evanananana", "author_id": "52590313868", "id": "18010369925831507", "text": "this is just french", "timestamp": 1770536267}, {"author": "abby.e.waugh", "author_id": "74532554253", "id": "18054070865442692", "text": "swedish chef coded", "timestamp": 1770215616}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/619684413_918760730480173_89362341521386743_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEeVmS4R8Bj7AR9VFY2bObbDRjRCBIg4tPOpj8O05kFxM6eoZqGuzuzcAESmn6uoog&_nc_ohc=N-uz2XPhhUgQ7kNvw